Depends: arc-theme, at, jq, rename, slick-greeter, wasta-core-focal, wasta-papirus, wasta-resources, wmctrl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: arc-solid-theme, wasta-vertex-ubuntu
Conflicts: gdm3
Description: Wasta-Linux MultiDesktop
 Ensures cross-desktop compatibility between different desktop sessions.
 A lightdm script is executed on login to make necessary adjustments based
 on detected session in comparison to previously detected session.
 .
 Currently only GNOME, Cinnamon, and XFCE are supported.
